UPDATE:

It installed fine under XP OS.

Now that I'm trying Windows 7 I installed from a USB device and it required the disc.  I then dragged it to the Hard Drive and it's installing.

I'm not 100% sure, but on the USB device I set the English to North America - no go, needed disc.  Installing from the hard drive with international language it didn't ask for the disc.

I would definitely install from the hard drive.  Maybe this is well known, but just putting it out there.
